result.notes: This survey was undertaken by Cefas as part of the CEFAS Historic surveys; ... Survey took place between 27/08/1970 and 06/09/1970 on Clione Equipment used during this survey : - Granton 60mm Cod End Bunt and Door Chains Codend Catch - Granton 60mm Cod End Bunt and Door Chains Cover Catch - Granton 60mm Cod End Bunt Chain Codend Catch - Granton 60mm Cod End Bunt Chain Cover Catch - Granton 60mm Cod End No Chains Codend Catch - Granton 60mm Cod End No Chains Cover Catch - Original Petersen Grab - Otter Trawl 78ft Granton with door to door chain and 60mm codend - Otter Trawl 78ft Granton with door to door chain and 60mm codend cover only Survey operations were undertaken on 56 stations 28 different species were caught on this survey
